rows.label: qst0000010_msg0002
rows.name: No, I get it. Don't say another word.

rows.label: qst0000010_msg0003
rows.name:
That gloomy face... You couldn't
salvage any treasure, could you?

rows.label: qst0000010_msg0004
rows.name:
Salvaging is like fishing. Sometimes
you get nothing, it happens. You'll
hit the jackpot again soon enough.

rows.label: qst0000010_msg0005
rows.name:
It's been half a year
since my last big haul...

rows.label: qst0000010_msg0006
rows.name: Half a year!? Man, that's hopeless...

rows.label: qst0000010_msg0007
rows.name:
Nah, nah, there are salvagers like that out
there. Ever hear the story about the son of
the brother of the uncle of Bawn's cousin?

rows.label: qst0000010_msg0008
rows.name:
The guy had no luck for three years straight, but
he kept at it. On the first day of his fourth year,
he found the best treasure he'd ever seen.

rows.label: qst0000010_msg0009
rows.name:
He salvaged treasure worth over a
billion G even back then! He became
the richest guy in Avaritia overnight!

rows.label: qst0000010_msg0010
rows.name:
So, Rex... It's too early to be
giving up after just half a year.

rows.label: qst0000010_msg0011
rows.name: I'll find some treasure next time!

rows.label: qst0000010_msg0012
rows.name:
Yeah, that's the spirit!
When you're young, you've
gotta stay positive.

rows.label: qst0000010_msg0013
rows.name:
I want to hear more about
that get-rich-quick story.

rows.label: qst0000010_msg0014
rows.name:
I don't know any more than
what I just told you. You
should ask Bawn for the details.
